# Documentation sync

- **Source of truth**: `production_api/main.py`, `production_api/tts_engine.py`, `production_api/Dockerfile`, and `docker-compose.yml`.
- **Docs**: English only under [`doc/`](/doc); update [`doc/deployment.md`](doc/deployment.md) when behavior or contracts change.
- **README**: Keep [`README.md`](README.md) aligned with the actual layout, env vars, and commands; avoid duplicating long deployment details already in `doc/deployment.md`.
- When unsure, load the personal Agent Skill **technical-docs-sync** (`~/.cursor/skills/technical-docs-sync/SKILL.md`) for workflow and checklists.
